                            </MadCap:dropDownHead>
                            <MadCap:dropDownBody>
                                <p>You can select one of the options for setting a break inside the "rendering box" of the element.<ul class="FirstLevel"><li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Automatic </span><MadCap:snippetText src="../../Shared/Co-Fl/Paragraphs/Break-Inside-Automatic.flsnp" /></li><li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Avoid </span><MadCap:snippetText src="../../Shared/Co-Fl/Paragraphs/Break-Inside-Avoid.flsnp" /></li></ul></p>
